This paper deals with the problem of inverse reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses experiments in gridworld environments and simulated robotics benchmarks, which are common topics in the sub-categories of machine learning, robotics, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
